// Incomming SMTP connection listener settings
String, smtp_incomming_username,,The username to be used if authenticating a client to the MessageVortex outgoing SMTP node
string, smtp_incomming_password,, The password to be used if authenticating a client to the MessageVortex outgoing SMTP node
boolean, smtp_incomming_ssl,false, True if the incomming smtp port is ssl wrapped.
numeric, smtp_incomming_port, 587, The port number for incomming smtp connects.
String, smtp_incomming_address,0.0.0.0, The listening Address to bind the server for incomming SMTP connects.



